```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_AWS-LLM-SageMaker
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

package "AWS LLM SageMaker RAG Workflow" {
  rectangle "Streamlit UI" {
    rectangle "Q&A Chatbot Interface" as ChatbotUI #lightyellow
  }

  rectangle "Inference & Serving" {
    rectangle "SageMaker Endpoint" as SagemakerEndpoint #lightblue
    rectangle "DJLServing & DeepSpeed" as DJLServing #lightblue
  }
  
  rectangle "Fine-Tuning & Model Management" {
    rectangle "QLoRA Fine-Tuning" as QLoRA #lightgreen
    rectangle "KoLLMSageMakerEndpoint" as KoLLEndpoint #lightgreen
  }

  rectangle "Retrieval & Embedding" {
    rectangle "Amazon Opensearch" as Opensearch #lightpink
    rectangle "FAISS Vector Search" as FAISS #lightpink
  }
  
  rectangle "Utility Functions" {
    rectangle "Inference Library" as InferenceLib #lightgray
    rectangle "Prompter Class" as Prompter #lightgray
    rectangle "Callback Handlers" as Callbacks #lightgray
  }
}

User --> ChatbotUI : Interacts
ChatbotUI --> SagemakerEndpoint : Query
SagemakerEndpoint --> Opensearch : Retrieve Documents
Opensearch --> SagemakerEndpoint : Return Documents
SagemakerEndpoint --> DJLServing : Process Query
DJLServing --> SagemakerEndpoint : Return Answer
SagemakerEndpoint --> ChatbotUI : Display Answer

QLoRA --> KoLLEndpoint : Fine-Tune Model
KoLLEndpoint --> SagemakerEndpoint : Deploy Model

InferenceLib --> SagemakerEndpoint : Manage Inference
Prompter --> InferenceLib : Generate Prompts
Callbacks --> InferenceLib : Stream Output
FAISS --> Opensearch : Vector Search
@enduml
```